{"type":"message","id":"740ac42b","parentId":"e795c4d9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:53:58.712Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session in the last 5 minutes is this cron job itself. There are no other active user conversations. I should execute the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services - industries relevant to 道简网络 (Daojian Network).","thinkingSignature":"a90fc30f15362b1aee62b650e8e2c59492a57df650e6217b63d790a71ae241f2"},{"type":"text","text":"没有活跃对话，执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_snvg69k7s3fr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":841,"output":117,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44939,"cost":{"input":0.0002523,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017121299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775058834697}}
{"type":"message","id":"75bd4fb9","parentId":"740ac42b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:53:58.718Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_snvg69k7s3fr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775058838715}}
{"type":"message","id":"80b3c40f","parentId":"75bd4fb9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:54:03.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for relevant industry news. I'll run multiple searches in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"90ea55a7d9a5cff061c01b6f69fc30b2d4b774ee7f93d53e8eefcb147f7f59f8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ci0hhmw5rjh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新动态 政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ci0hhmw5rjh_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业 2026 最新动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ci0hhmw5rjh_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026 最新趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1473,"output":193,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45647,"cost":{"input":0.00044189999999999995,"output":0.0002316,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00199293}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775058838718}}
